                                      12      12.     ********************************************************************
                                      13      13.     *                                                                  *
                                      14      14.     *  FILMAINT is the driver program for running ORVYL file system    *
                                      15      15.     *  maintenance.  It will attach the necessary utilities to dump    *
                                      16      16.     *  the file system catalog, verify the IXR record structure, dump  *
                                      17      17.     *  the IXR records, and dump the actual file system.               *
                                      18      18.     *                                                                  *
                                      19      19.     ********************************************************************
                                      20      20.     *                                                                  *
                                      21      21.     *  Exec field parameters:                                          *
                                      22      22.     *                                                                  *
                                      23      23.     *        FSNAME     ORVYL file system name                         *
                                      24      24.     *        ORVNAME    Name of ORVYL to communicate with              *
                                      25      25.     *        DUMP       Perform full file dump                         *
                                      26      26.     *        VERIFY     Perform file system verify                     *
                                      27      27.     *        INCTAPE    Perform incremental dump to tape               *
                                      28      28.     *        INCDISK    Perform incremental dump to disk               *
                                      29      29.     *                                                                  *
                                      30      30.     *                                                                  *
                                      31      31.     ********************************************************************
                                      32      32.     *                                                                  *
                                      33      33.     *  Return codes:                                                   *
                                      34      34.     *                                                                  *
                                      35      35.     *              0  -  File maintenance completed successfully       *
                                      36      36.     *              4  -  Completed successfully, warnings issued       *
                                      37      37.     *              8  -  Completed successfully, error messages issued *
                                      38      38.     *             12  -  Maintenance terminated by operator            *
                                      39      39.     *             16  -  File system maintenance has failed            *
                                      40      40.     *             20  -  Internal logic error                          *
                                      41      41.     *                                                                  *
                                      42      42.     *                                                                  *
                                      43      43.     ********************************************************************

                                   18383    1043.32   Ÿ  Compute elapsed time in (.01) second units from a starting         Ÿ
                                   18384    1043.33   Ÿ  and ending SMF format time/date pairs.  This routine is Y2K        Ÿ

                                   18389    1043.38   Ÿ    Entry:    R1 - Address of a four word list                       Ÿ
                                   18390    1043.39   Ÿ                   +0 SMF format starting time                       Ÿ
